title: Senior Bowl Practice Recap & Interviews
itunes:title: Senior Bowl Practice Recap & Interviews
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis are back with a special episode from the Senior Bowl. To start off, the guys recap the day of practice and talk about a few players they are intrigued by (1:35). Then, DJ and Bucky interview Utah State QB Jordan Love (9:10). After that, DJ talks with Jaguars GM David Caldwell about the franchise (18:01). To wrap up the show, DJ and Bucky speak with Alabama edge rusher Terrell Lewis (26:31).
